: -- Compile & Run --------
    make
    ./books
: -- Controls
    1,2,3,4 : see different objects and scenes
    esc : exit
    0   : reset view angle
    up/down/right/light : change view angle
    page up/down : zoom in/out
    a   : Toggle axes
    l   : Toggle lighting
    m   : Stop light source
    []  : move light source
